<p>Oral administration works best for gut inflammation. KPV pairs exceptionally well with probiotics, as it calms the immune environment while beneficial bacteria recolonize the gut.</p>

<p>Many practitioners combine KPV with BPC-157 for a dual-action approach: KPV stops the inflammatory damage while BPC-157 repairs what's already been harmed.</p>

